text: Greenland has five municipalities (): Avannaata, Kujalleq, Qeqertalik, Qeqqata, and Sermersooq.Statistics Greenland, Greenland in Figures, 2014 The Northeast Greenland National Park is not part of any municipality and is an unincorporated area.
